            "title": "黑期低水逾百點 重磅港股ADR僅滙控與京東向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時17分跌76點或0.28%，報26871點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報26878點，較香港上日現貨收市低121點或0.45%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣632.6元，較上日香港收市低0.43元或0.07%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣165.6元，較上日香港收市低3.41元或2.02%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣101元，較上日香港收市低0.53元或0.52%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣116.3元，較上日香港收市高0.39元或0.34%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣37.6元，較上日香港收市低0.15元或0.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣127.5元，較上日香港收市高0.5元或0.39%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣84.6元，較上日香港收市低0.12元或0.14%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣433.9元，較上日香港收市低0.9元或0.21%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣68.5元，較上日香港收市低0.24元或0.35%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.7元，較上日香港收市低0.04元或0.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指期貨夜市收報26901點，跌73點，較上日恒指收市26999點，低水99點。科指期貨夜市收報5858點，較上日科指收市低水50點；國指期貨夜市收報9276點，較上日國指收市低水40點。</p>\n</div>",
